itunes:title: Beauty And The Bride
title: Beauty And The Bride
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew hang out with Allie Laree, an Arizona based hair and makeup artist who travels the worlds making over brides for their big day. She has built her business from the ground up and does it all while being a mama! She is also launching new education to help the every day woman to perfect her makeup routine. You also hear Stew confess his love for James Charles... so let's just say this episode is entertaining to say the least!
